<% content_for :page_title, "문항 관리" %>

<div class="rp-page-header">
  <h1 class="rp-page-header__title">문항 관리</h1>
  <p class="rp-page-header__subtitle">진단에 포함될 문항을 관리합니다</p>
</div>

<div class="rp-info-box">
  <p>문항 관리는 <strong>문항개발자(Researcher)</strong> 포털에서 수행됩니다.</p>
  <%= link_to "문항개발자 포탈 → 문항관리", "/researcher/item_bank", class: "rp-btn rp-btn--primary", target: "_blank" %>
</div>

<style>
  .rp-page-header {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .rp-page-header__title {
    font-size: var(--rp-font-size-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  }

  .rp-page-header__subtitle {
    font-size: var(--rp-font-size-base);
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .rp-info-box {
    background: #eff6ff;
    border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .rp-info-box p {
    font-size: var(--rp-font-size-base);
    color: #0369a1;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .rp-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: var(--rp-font-size-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }

  .rp-btn--primary {
    background: #2f5bff;
    color: white;
  }

  .rp-btn--primary:hover {
    background: #1e4ae8;
  }
</style>
